author: Elizabeth Chuck and Erika Edwards
title: Can you catch the coronavirus twice? What's known about immunity
description: Those who recover from the coronavirus will likely have protection against getting reinfected by the illness, experts believe, although it is unclear how long that immunity can be expected to last.
content:
Those who recover from the coronavirus are probably not going to catch the illness again, at least in the short term, experts say. But it's unclear how long that immunity will last.
